DialogueTexts.Text: Was that a dream?
Weird. I don't remember lying down yet.
Where did I leave my pills?
I really should take my pills, right now.
Thank God I have these.
My mind was really messed up.
I thought I had more pills.
How many did I take last night?
What was that earlier?
It didn't feel like a dream.
But it gave me chills.
Well, I need to get some sleep.
I really should get some sleep now.
I miss her.
She meant everything to me.
I'm not hungry right now.
It's late for supper.
Does this really have nine thousand games in one?
I'll pick them up later.
I dont't have matches.
Why would I light a candle now?
